. IN NS
SECTION ANSWER
. IN NS	K.ROOT-SERVERS.NET.
SECTION ADDITIONAL
K.ROOT-SERVERS.NET.	IN	A	127.0.0.3
ENTRY_END

ENTRY_BEGIN
MATCH opcode subdomain
ADJUST copy_id copy_query
REPLY QR NOERROR
