a.gtld-servers.net.	IN	A
SECTION ANSWER
a.gtld-servers.net.	IN 	A	127.0.0.4
ENTRY_END

ENTRY_BEGIN
MATCH opcode qtype qname
ADJUST copy_id copy_query
REPLY QR NOERROR
SECTION QUESTION
a.gtld-servers.net.	IN	AAAA
SECTION AUTHORITY
. SOA bla bla 1 2 3 4 5
